{"tid":2355489,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"17 歲男被指管雷射筆　事隔逾一年遭起訴　今提堂准保釋","createTime":"2021-01-06T06:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T09:18:13.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ae59f4ee08d2abc1f566b4f0142f133438b2495","tid":2355489,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"前年 9 月 8 日，有市民於遮打花園參與「香港人權與民主祈禱會」，隨後警方以武力清場。 17 歲男學生被指藏有雷射筆，遭控「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」罪。事隔一年多，今（6日）首次在東區裁判法院提堂。主任裁判官錢禮押後案件至 3 月 23 日再提訊，以待辯方索取文件及法律意見。被告獲准以 1000 元保釋，須每週往警署報到一次，及居於報稱地址。<br />\n<br />\n17歲車姓男學生，被控一項「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」罪，指他在 2019 年 9 月 8 日，在中環雪廠街外的公眾地方，無合法權限或合理辯解而攜有一個能發出雷射光束的裝置。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC25/2021"},{"pid":"15cc01ceed71fabc3689be7cb0a8a5f54554afd2","tid":2355489,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/17-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E7%AE%A1%E9%9B%B7%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86-%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-%E4%BB%8A%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F17-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E9%259B%25B7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImbyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=266c08d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F17-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E9%259B%25B7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%